data.description: WELCOME to this beautiful all brick rancher with a fully fenced back yard, new roof, heat pump, a huge shed to place all of your tools, and a beautiful deck. It comes with a brand new washer and dryer in unit, laminate flooring all throughout the living room and your 2 bedrooms 1 bathroom. Come and take a look at this home! This property is owner occupied and will only be available for showings on Sundays from 9:00AM - 6:00PM.
